{"tid":1042983,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"支那竟有人花錢為貓割雙眼皮 網友齊砲轟","createTime":"2019-03-02T02:25:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-02T05:20:34.000Z","uid":2547,"like":0,"dislike":48,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"0972c72fcc50433fad76650b7524b20705bba99c","tid":1042983,"uid":2547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T02:25:57.000Z","msg":"整型已經越來越普遍，但這股整型風潮在中國竟然也吹向寵物界。中國媒體報導，江蘇南京近日有民眾指出，有人花了人民幣1萬元（約1500美元）給貓動了雙眼皮手術。對此，不少網友表示無法理解這種已屬於虐貓的行為，並批評貓主人，「你考慮過貓的感受嗎？」<br />\n據江蘇新聞網報導，南京一位民眾表示，自己在翻看微信朋友圈時，看到一個朋友發出的照片，照片上寵物貓剛做完雙眼皮手術，眼睛還是呈現紅腫狀態，而且貓咪看上去狀況也很不好，有點奄奄一息的感覺。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/02/102522_66931bedd7e2ebf9d7504805116dfda7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F02%2F102522_66931bedd7e2ebf9d7504805116dfda7.png&h=553ebb3d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n從相片中可以看出來，這隻可憐的貓咪做完手術後非常虛弱，而且眼睛周圍的毛都被剃光了，貓眼上還有縫合傷口的線。據稱，貓主人這麼做純粹是為了讓自己的貓咪能「更美」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/02/102548_1c0e1887da1583e11f6075cee0e93d37.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F02%2F102548_1c0e1887da1583e11f6075cee0e93d37.png&h=552f7189&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n上海《澎湃新聞》實地走訪南京多家寵物醫院，部分醫院確實表示可以為寵物進行整型手術。其中一家寵物醫院表示，之前一般會給特定品種或是要參加比賽的狗做雙眼皮手術。<br />\n<br />\n但也有寵物醫院工作人員表示，為寵物進行整型手術可能會產生併發症，一些寵物醫院則表示抵制這類手術。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://video.udn.com/news/1028486\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvideo.udn.com%2Fnews%2F1028486&d=u7xsq8u58TeopDPyjGw7C2zUwbN2nhMFbUYjFdDHJd4%3D&h=c589d627\" target=\"_blank\">https://video.udn.com/news/1028486</a>"},{"pid":"f37564a0157be53bfef052f3d0c0df2a0ae7aaa1","tid":1042983,"uid":85219,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T02:30:17.000Z","msg":"Cls 大陸人真係無腦"},{"pid":"0bbd2edd9c630ee66fe723fcee0e538a18bb8369","tid":1042983,"uid":140302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T02:31:05.000Z","msg":"On9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5421e76c1f8a987432b14789e7a1fe210e4a7edb","tid":1042983,"uid":90704,"like":2,"dislike":11,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T02:39:29.000Z","msg":"Ho ball<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n激死啲動物撚"},{"pid":"a8c33cdf1238560f2cc5f41c6c1638561c8fc38d","tid":1042983,"uid":28580,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T02:45:21.000Z","msg":"跟車太貼<br />\n你睇多d新聞先好轉貼"},{"pid":"62c4457fdece369150311ab4f93e0c824985160f","tid":1042983,"uid":129521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T03:11:50.000Z","msg":"連登仔唔好柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa8e350f7f5a9282583f2bb14c416772f53528b4","tid":1042983,"uid":49853,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T03:27:36.000Z","msg":"對眼咁撚大仲要割雙眼皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a96e56cf3a44a8544d1c59edbc071bc5899f520c","tid":1042983,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T04:20:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d535b7df8e0a6782688e244a7c0e18584a1922ce","tid":1042983,"uid":39215,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T04:22:51.000Z","msg":"中國人呢個民族 真係毫無人性可言<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be42098127e5263d0a5abbf33f448b27f55efb58","tid":1042983,"uid":27038,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T04:24:35.000Z","msg":"屌你，呢啲仆街幾時死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b75e8bf5221e07e29741e375de96c9413889d4b7","tid":1042983,"uid":130901,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T04:26:42.000Z","msg":"獸醫竟然話狗割雙腿皮比較多<br />\n<br />\n不過再諗支那連人權都無，動物感受更無人理啦"},{"pid":"56cbdeeac61fa310afee289cdc40fd3c706b0d8c","tid":1042983,"uid":181111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T05:09:53.000Z","msg":"好可憐...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"659040a79831fa55394d02a4d677e03e3d57e717","tid":1042983,"uid":3818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T05:19:44.000Z","msg":"支那又領先世紀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c08d18f75807dd4cecf70ca8fa458a5336426f24","tid":1042983,"uid":51720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"62c4457fdece369150311ab4f93e0c824985160f","tid":1042983,"uid":129521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T03:11:50.000Z","msg":"連登仔唔好柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T05:20:34.000Z","msg":"笑話：豬都會割雙眼皮啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}